Column3:
Represent the World Health Organization performance status at t0: 
- 0: Asymptomatic;
- 1: Symptomatic but completely ambulatory;
- 2: Symptomatic, <50% in bed during the day;
- 3: Symptomatic, >50% in bed, but not bedbound;
- 4: Bedbound;
- 5: Dead.

